\c 4
\s Kusiyana nezvivi
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo Kristu zvaakatitamburira panyama, nemwi muzvishongedze nemurangariro wakadaro; nokuti iye watambudzika panyama, aregedzwa pachivi;
\v 2 kuti nguva yasara panyama musachiraramira kuchiva kwevanhu, asi chido chaMwari.
\v 3 Nokuti yakatiringana nguva yakapfuura yeupenyu kuita chido chevahedheni, patakafamba mukusazvibata, kuchiva, kuraradza, makaro, \add ne\add*mitambo yekunwa, nekunamata zvifananidzo zvisingatenderwi;
\v 4 zvavanoshamisika mazviri, kuti hamumhanyidzani \add navo\add* pakuwandisa kumwe kwenyonga-nyonga, vachi\add ku\add*tuka\add i\add*;
\v 5 vachazvidavirira kuna iye wakagadzirira kutonga vapenyu nevakafa.
\v 6 Nokuti nekuda kwaizvozvi evhangeri yakaparidzirwa kune vakafawo, kuti vatongwe zvinoenderana nevanhu panyama, asi vararame zvinoenderana naMwari pamweya.
\s Chenjerai nokuti kuguma kwava pedo
\p
\v 7 Zvino kuguma kwezvinhu zvose kwaswedera; naizvozvo svinurai murinde muminyengetero.
\v 8 Uye mberi kwezvinhu zvose ivai nerudo rwunopfuta pakati penyu, nokuti rudo ruchafukidzira zvivi zvizhinji-zhinji.
\v 9 Gamuchiranai, pasina kunyunyuta.
\v 10 Umwe neumwe sezvaakagamuchira chipo, shumiranai ichocho sevatariri vakanaka venyasha dzakasiyana-siyana dzaMwari.
\v 11 Kana umwe achitaura, \add ngaataure\add* semashoko aMwari; kana umwe achishumira \add ngazviitwe\add* sezvinobva kusimba Mwari raanopa; kuti Mwari akudzwe pazvinhu zvose kubudikidza naJesu Kristu, kwaari kune kukudzwa nesimba kusvika rinhi narinhi. Ameni.
\p
\v 12 Vadiwa, musashamisika nemuedzo unopisa uri pamuri unokuidzai, sezvinonzi mawirwa nechisingazikanwi;
\v 13 asi sezvamuri vagovani vematambudziko aKristu, farai, kuti nepakuratidzwa kwekubwinya kwake mufare nemufaro mukurusa.
\v 14 Kana muchitukwa nekuda kwezita raKristu, makaropafadzwa; nokuti Mweya wekubwinya newaMwari agere pamusoro penyu; kwavari zvirokwazvo anonyombwa, asi kwamuri anokudzwa.
\v 15 Asi kusava neumwe wenyu anotambudzika semhondi, kana mbavha, kana muiti wezvakaipa, kana anongongwarira zvevamwe;
\v 16 asi kana \add achitambudzika\add* semuKristu, asanyara; asi ngaakudze Mwari pachinhu ichi.
\v 17 Nokuti yava nguva yekuti kutonga kutange paimba yaMwari; zvino kana kukatanga kwatiri, kuguma kwevasingateereri evhangeri yaMwari kuchavei?
\v 18 Uye kana wakarurama achiponeswa nemutsutsururu, asingadi Mwari nemutadzi vachaonekera papi?
\v 19 Naizvozvo naivo vanotambudzika zvinoenderana nechido chaMwari, sekuMusiki wakatendeka ngavakumikidze mweya yavo pakuita zvakanaka.
